类：org/springframework/web/servlet/handler/AbstractHandlerMethodMapping.java

```
protected void initHandlerMethods() {
		if (logger.isDebugEnabled()) {
			logger.debug("Looking for request mappings in application context: " + getApplicationContext());
		}

		String[] beanNames = (this.detectHandlerMethodsInAncestorContexts ?
				BeanFactoryUtils.beanNamesForTypeIncludingAncestors(getApplicationContext(), Object.class) :
				getApplicationContext().getBeanNamesForType(Object.class));

		for (String beanName : beanNames) {
			if (isHandler(getApplicationContext().getType(beanName))){
				detectHandlerMethods(beanName);
			}
		}
		handlerMethodsInitialized(getHandlerMethods());
	}
```


在这个方法中，会遍历所有的bean，如果是Controller则会做RequestMapping。这里面的关键方法是isHandler(beanClassType)；进入这个方法：

```
protected boolean isHandler(Class<?> beanType) {
		return ((AnnotationUtils.findAnnotation(beanType, Controller.class) != null) ||
				(AnnotationUtils.findAnnotation(beanType, RequestMapping.class) != null));
	}
```

会检查类是否有Controller标注或者RequestMapping标注。这里传入的beanType是代理对象的类型。
具体findAnnotation的代码也顺便贴一下：

```
public static <A extends Annotation> A findAnnotation(Class<?> clazz, Class<A> annotationType) {
		Assert.notNull(clazz, "Class must not be null");
		A annotation = clazz.getAnnotation(annotationType);
		if (annotation != null) {
			return annotation;
		}
		for (Class<?> ifc : clazz.getInterfaces()) {
			annotation = findAnnotation(ifc, annotationType);
			if (annotation != null) {
				return annotation;
			}
		}
		if (!Annotation.class.isAssignableFrom(clazz)) {
			for (Annotation ann : clazz.getAnnotations()) {
				annotation = findAnnotation(ann.annotationType(), annotationType);
				if (annotation != null) {
					return annotation;
				}
			}
		}
		Class<?> superclass = clazz.getSuperclass();
		if (superclass == null || superclass.equals(Object.class)) {
			return null;
		}
		return findAnnotation(superclass, annotationType);
	}
```

在这个过程中，如果是Cglib的代理对象的类型，则可以通过superclass找到原来的Controller类，如果是Jdk的代理对象的类型，就找不到了。

